  author   = "Garc{\'\i}a-Garc{\'\i}a, Isabel and Kube, Jana and Morys, Filip
              and Schrimpf, Anne and Kanaan, A S Ahmad S and Gaebler, Michael
              and Villringer, Arno and Dagher, Alain and Horstmann, Annette and
              Neumann, Jane",
  abstract = "\copyright{} 2019, The Psychonomic Society, Inc. Emotions can
              influence our eating behaviors. Facing an acute stressor or being
