              overweight individuals can reduce high-calorie food evaluation,
              but also neural activations in inhibitory control- and reward-
              related brain regions.",
  journal  = "Soc. Cogn. Affect. Neurosci.",
  month    =  dec,
  year     =  2021,
  keywords = "f MRI; food evaluation; food-specific inhibition training;
              overweight;Mendeley Import (Jul 28);MyPapers"
}

